gate: OPEN
sprint: S05
track: B
task: B5
title: "feat(notifications): shipment-tracking notifications CNH + CNH-DFS (#981)"
repos: [crop-front]
priority: high
refs:
  - CROP-front#981
  - CROP-front#978  (parent umbrella)
  - CROP-front#1428 (confirmation email fire-and-forget — related reliability concern)
  - CROP-front#1396 (RESEND_API_KEY missing — must be confirmed resolved before merge)
requires: [NEXTJS_VERCEL_FRONTEND]

description: |
  Customers on CNH and CNH-DFS lanes receive no shipment-tracking notification.
  Trigger a tracking email via Resend when a tracking number appears on these lanes.
  Pre-condition: #1396 (RESEND_API_KEY missing in Vercel prod) confirmed resolved.
  Notification send must NOT be fire-and-forget (lesson from #1428).

scope:
  in:
    - Trigger: tracking number written to order record for CNH / CNH-DFS
    - Notification: email via Resend with tracking link + carrier
    - Idempotency: no duplicate on unchanged tracking number
    - Staging verify: trigger CNH order → confirm notification received
  out:
    - UPS-lane tracking (separate system)
    - Order confirmation email (#1428)

invariants:
  - Must NOT be fire-and-forget — use durable dispatch or confirm delivery
  - RESEND_API_KEY confirmed in Vercel prod before merge

acceptance:
  - CNH order ships → tracking email sent with correct link
  - CNH-DFS same
  - Duplicate tracking number → no duplicate notification
  - Staging smoke documented in PR

dep: B4 + #1396 resolved
output: notification trigger + idempotency guard + staging smoke note in PR
